{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Introduction</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Type</strong>: Text-based Sandbox Survival Game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Setting</strong>: The Realm of Valhallastarves</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When the protagonist awakens, they find themselves in the Realm of the Einherjar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the newest guardian of this primal purgatory, your mission is to defeat Odin\u2019s enemies and bring order to the divine realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Creative Building, Abundant Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start from nothing in this sandbox survival world. Use all the resources around you to construct essential and unique facilities, such as beds, barbecue grills, chopping blocks, cauldrons, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345500/extras/building2.gif?t=1734999013\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Challenging Survival, Explore the Divine Realm</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore diverse maps, from grasslands to forests, snow-capped mountains, and plains. Collect resources, hunt various monsters, and fight to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345500/extras/hunt.gif?t=1734999013\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Pet Training, Relaxing Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You won\u2019t be alone on your journey. Raise up to 261 pet birds, each with unique skills to assist you in your adventures. Feed them, enjoy their melodious songs, and relax your mind along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345500/extras/bird.gif?t=1734999013\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Content You Can Experience in The Valhallastarves</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Build 20 types of functional structures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Upgrade buildings and research construction technologies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Explore 17 adventure maps and 3 dungeon maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Gather various resources on the maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Defeat monsters and beasts in the environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Complete NPC commissions for rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Craft weapons, armor, food, and medicine from materials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Train 261 unique pet birds with special traits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Trade goods with merchants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Enjoy other gameplay features, with regular updates coming soon!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Friendly Reminder</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25b6 If you are looking for stunning visuals, this game may not meet your expectations, as it does not feature elaborate graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25b6 If you encounter any issues during gameplay or have suggestions and ideas, feel free to contact me anytime.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\u91c7\u6c34\u4eba","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3345500/750ba3dc152f372aec313a4528b6641c4f70df77.jpg"},{"name":"\u4f10\u6728\u5de5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3345500/5c0160faf26a1624156688cafdf195409c361fd1.jpg"},{"name":"\u6253\u6e14\u4eba","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3345500/4a74e7f66eae08b19403af2dc86f61418b74595f.jpg"},{"name":"\u730e\u9e7f\u4eba","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3345500/98c3a5e47ea2ae73994639c9d5905609e5a07e76.jpg"},{"name":"\u89c5\u98df\u8005","path":"https://cdn.a