><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Explore 17 adventure maps and 3 dungeon maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Gather various resources on the maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Defeat monsters and beasts in the environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Complete NPC commissions for rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Craft weapons, armor, food, and medicine from materials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Train 261 unique pet birds with special traits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Trade goods with merchants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Enjoy other gameplay features, with regular updates coming soon!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Friendly Reminder</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25b6 If you are looking for stunning visuals, this game may not meet your expectations, as it does not feature elaborate graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25b6 If you encounter any issues during gameplay or have suggestions and ideas, feel free to contact me anytime.</p>","developers":["\u9965\u997f\u6bbf\u4e3b"],"dlc":[3380710],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345500/header.jpg?t=1734999013","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257080125,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257080125/movie480.mp4?t=1733709415","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257080125/movie_max.mp4?t=1733709415"},"name":"valhallastarves","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257080125/05436d24e10bad9e158562734a275dc8f9a0830b/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1733709415","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_